				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: What Trade Skill Should a Bard be good at?<a name="69816"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Nov 16 04 12:28 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Get your brewing to max 252.  At that point, create the trophy - Grandmaster Brewer's corker.  (This is not an easy item to create, but not impossible).  Right click on the trophy to summon a no-rent bag.  Hand said bag to the gnome on the balcony in the building in the bazaar - he will give you back a 10slot, 100% wr bag.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
