				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: What Trade Skill Should a Bard be good at?<a name="69832"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Nov 16 04 3:02 PM</span></td>
