				<td colspan="2"><span>Yeah, I just made Minotaur Hero Brews the whole way. No stats and don't sell on the open market, but the components can all be bought in the same room in Ak'Anon (except the water, which is in the next room) and trivs at 248. It's a 9 component combine, but once you get a success and add it to your favorites, it's easy.
<br />

<br />
EDIT: Forgot to mention that even though MHB's don't sell in the open market, you can sell them back to the vendor you buy your components from to make back some of the overhead costs. That's why it only cost me 300pp to go to 219 (high CHA and faction song helps also). You'll probably need a shrink device to move around without any troubles. I'm a Vah Shir and had to duck to get into the room with the brew barrel. After I shrank in the room before it though, I had no problems.</span></td>
