				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: What Trade Skill Should a Bard be good at?<a name="69973"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Nov 18 04 6:27 PM</span></td>
