				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: What Trade Skill Should a Bard be good at?<a name="70370"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Nov 27 04 5:42 PM</span></td>
