				<td colspan="2"><span>eqtraders.com is your friend if you want to tradeskill.  Go there.  Check out in particular their guides on how to quickly raise each skill.
<br />

<br />
I've found that it's handy to know as much as you can on all of the tradeskills.  There are frequently times when you need to make something using another skill in order to do what you want.
<br />

<br />
I have also found that the Abysmal Sea is the best place to do the work.  If something for tradeskilling can be purchased from a vendor, 99% of the time someone on the boat sells it.</span></td>
